hermit: hermit (terminal emulator)
hermit:
hermit: Small terminal emulator configurable via Lua.
hermit: Other dependencies are Vte and Gtk2 libs.
hermit: Hermit supports multiple tabs, encoding switching and sessions.
hermit: 
